0year%20for%20the%20next%20decade%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20forecast%20is%20down%20from%207%25%20last%20year%20and%207.2%25%20heading%20into%202023%2C%20though%20it's%20higher%20than%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falternative-investing-strategy-60-40-portfolio-bitcoin-outlook-inflation-jpmorgan-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E4.3%25%20mark%20in%20late%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20US%20large%20caps%20were%20only%20expected%20to%20climb%204.1%25%20a%20year%20in%20the%20long%20term%20after%20an%20outstanding%20rebound%20from%20the%20early%20pandemic%20lows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBonds%2C%20which%20make%20up%20the%20second%20half%20of%20that%20calculus%2C%20have%20a%20solid%20but%20unremarkable%20outlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20bonds%20broadly%20are%20expected%20to%20return%204.6%25%20in%20the%20long%20term%20%E2%80%94%20down%20from%205.1%25%20last%20year%20and%20the%20same%20as%20two%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20while%20the%20US%2010-year%20Treasury%20note%20is%20projected%20to%20fetch%204.2%25%2C%20versus%204.6%25%20last%20year%20and%204%25%20two%20years%20ago.%20Meanwhile%2C%20high-yield%20bonds%20should%20deliver%20a%206.1%25%20gain%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20compared%20to%206.5%25%20last%20year%20and%206.8%25%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20accounting%20for%20inflation%2C%20JPMAM%20expects%20the%20standard%2060-40%20portfolio%20to%20return%20less%20than%205%25%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20and%20the%20same%20is%20true%20of%20large-cap%20stocks%20and%20bonds.%20While%20such%20gains%20may%20be%20satisfactory%20for%20some%2C%20it%20would%20take%20over%2016%20years%20for%20an%20investor%20to%20double%20their%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20looking%20for%20a%20more%20compelling%20investment%20opportunity%20should%20consider%20real%20estate%2C%20according%20to%20JPMAM.%20Unlike%20stocks%20and%20bonds%2C%20the%20firm's%20projected%20returns%20for%20that%20asset%20class%20are%20steadily%20rising%2C%20from%