onference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommercial%20real%20estate%20looks%20especially%20compelling%2C%20Issar%20said.%20Unlike%20residential%20real%20estate%2C%20which%20has%20held%20up%20well%20in%20recent%20years%20%E2%80%94%20as%20evidenced%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FMSPUS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremarkably%20resilient%20home%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20despite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freddiemac.com%2Fpmms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estill-elevated%20mortgage%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20office%20buildings%20have%20struggled%20to%20regain%20their%20value%20since%20the%20pandemic%20ushered%20in%20a%20new%20era%20of%20remote%20work%20for%20millions%20of%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20companies%20reduced%20their%20physical%20presence%20or%20eschewed%20offices%20altogether%2C%20demand%20for%20commercial%20spaces%20has%20taken%20a%20massive%20hit.%20However%2C%20Issar%20thinks%20that%20risk%20is%20reflected%20in%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20we've%20been%20reading%20about%20and%20all%20we've%20been%20seeing%20is%20price%20declines%20and%20discussions%20about%20empty%20buildings%2C%26quot%3B%20Issar%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20time%20for%20investors%20to%20step%20in%2C%20move%20into%20attractive%20pricing%2C%20move%20into%20asset%20classes%20like%20non-core%20real%20estate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20can%20bet%20on%20a%20commercial%20real%20estate%20rebound%20by%20working%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fam.jpmorgan.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fasset-management%2Finstitutional%2Finvestment-strategies%2Falternatives%2Freal-estate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJPMAM's%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20on%20their%20own%20through%20publicly%20traded%20real%20estate%20investment%20trusts%20(REITs).%20JPMAM%20didn't%20outline%20any%20specific%20investments%20to%20make%2C%20but%20Issar%20threw%20out%20a%20few%20ideas%20to%20help%20investors%20brainstorm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20of%20multifamily%20housing%3B%20think%20of%20student%20housing%20around%20campuses%3B%20think%20of%20cell%20towers%20and%20data%20centers%2C%26quot%3B%20Issar%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20the%20modernization%20of%20the%20new%20direct%20real%20estate%20that%20is%20going%20to%20be%20really%20attractive%20for%20investors%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-strategy-real-estate-stocks-bonds-portfolio-jpmorgan-asset-management-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729677602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671812a9a0a0cc14f2231f7f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-strategy-real-estate-stocks-bonds-portfolio-jpmorgan-asset-management-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Goldman%20Sachs%20and%20JPMorgan%20Asset%20Management%20agree%20that%20long-term%20stock%20returns%20may%20be%20significantly%20lower%20%E2%80%94%20but%20real%20estate%20can%20pick%20up%20the%20slack.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jfaris%40businessinsider.com%20(James%20Faris)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-strategy-real-estate-stocks-bonds-portfolio-jpmorgan-asset-management-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20poisoned%20chalice%20of%20restaurant%20popularity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Server%20holding%20tray%20of%20food%20being%20knocked%20off%20by%20Michelin%20star%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6717df29a0a0cc14f22306ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EValentin%20Tkach%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-city-gaudy-gilded-age-restaurants-bars-wall-street-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDiscovering%20a%20great%20restaurant%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20thrilling%2C%20especially%20before%20it%20really%20takes%20off.%20It's%20delightful%20to%20scope%20out%20a%20fresh%20place%2C%20realize%20the%20food%20is%20amazing%2C%20and%20then%2C%20while%20you%20can%2C%20keep%20it%20a%20secret.%20That%20hidden%20gem%20down%20the%20quiet%20street%20is%20yours.%20For%20restaurants%2C%20though%2C%20%26quot%3Bhidden%20gem%26quot%3B%20status%20isn't%20always%20ideal.%20The%20industry%20is%20notoriously%20tough%2C%20and%20margins%20are%20razor-thin.%20And%20so%2C%20when%20a%20place%20blows%20up%20%E2%80%94%20because%20it%20gets%20an%20award%20or%20winds%20up%20on%20a%20best-of%20list%20or%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-food-reporter-tries-nyc-golden-corral-for-first-time-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20goes%20viral%20on%20TikTok%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20generally%20good%20news.%20Longtime%20customers%20may%20not%20love%20having%20to%20share%20their%20favorite%20spot%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20newbies%2C%20but%20restaurateurs%20need%20butts%20in%20seats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExcept%2C%20success%20can%20sometimes%20come%20back%20to%20bite%20the%20business.%20Getting%20good%20is%20one%20thing.%20Getting%20big%20is%20another%2C%20and%20not%20every%20operation%20is%20up%20to%20the%20task.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDaniel%20Sands%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20the%20University%20College%20London's%20School%20of%20Management%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdiscovery.ucl.ac.uk%2Fid%2Feprint%2F10195583%2F1%2FSands%2520SMJ%25202024%2520Michelin%2520stars%2520reactivity%2520and%2520restaurant%2520exits.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erecently%20took%20a%20look%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20the%20fates%20of%20New%20York%20City's%20most%20promising%20restaurants%20over%20the%20course%20of%20two%20decades%20to%20track%20how%20reviews%20from%20outside%20parties%20%E2%80%94%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20Michelin%20Guide%20%E2%80%94%20influenced%20the%20behaviors%20of%20the%20businesses.%20His%20findings%3A%20The%20brightest%20food-world%20stars%20tended%20to%20burn%20out%20faster.%20He%20tracked%20newly%20opened%20restaurants%20from%202000%20to%202014%20that%20got%20a%20starred%20review%20from%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20an%20early%20sign%20of%20critical%20success.%20He%20then%20looked%20at%20the%20diverging%20fortunes%20of%20those%20restaurants%20that%20went%20on%20to%20receive%20a%20Michelin%20star%20%E2%80%94%20a%20signifier%20of%20excellence%20in%20the%20industry.%20The%20award%2C%20however%2C%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20poisoned%20chalice%20for%20many%20winners.%20By%202019%2C%20Sands%20found%20that%20restaurants%20given%20a%20Michelin%20star%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20shutter.%20Blowing%20up%20changed%20things%20so%20much%20for%20some%20restaurants%20that%20it%20hurt%20as%20much%20as%2C%20or%20more%20than%2C%20it%20helped.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BMichelin%20stars%20aren't%20creating%20new%20pressures%20itself.%20What%20they%20seem%20to%20be%20doing%20is%20exacerbating%20the%20existing%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20Sands%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20the%20types%20of%20things%20that%20you'd%20be%20dealing%20with%20maybe%20at%20a%20slow%2C%20steady%20pace%20throughout%20your%20lifetime%20now%20seem%20to%20happen%20more%20rapidly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20publicity%20created%20around%20an%20award%20such%20as%20a%20Michelin%20star%20drives%20interest.%20Google%20searches%20for%20the%20restaurant%20increase%2C%20and%20new%20customers%20start%20coming%20in%2C%20including%20tourists.%20This%20is%20by%20and%20large%20a%20good%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20restaurants%20make%20money%20by%20serving%20people%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20can%20also%20be%20a%20challenge%20as%20consumer%20expectations%20become%20lofty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BTo%20meet%20these%20expectations%2C%20we'd%20see%20restaurateurs%20engage%20in%20different%20sorts%20of%20behaviors%2C%20everything%20from%20updating%20decor%20and%20service%20in%20ways%20that%20might%20not%20be%20revenue%20enhancing%20to%20a%20story%20of%20maybe%20displacing%20some%20of%20the%20regular%20customers%20that%20are%20a%20very%20important%20part%20of%20this%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Sands%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20a%20restaurant%20gains%20notoriety%2C%20other%20businesses%20it%20works%20with%20take%20note.%20Suppliers%20think%20they%20can%20charge%20more%2C%20landlords%20increase%20the%20rent%2C%20and%20chefs%20and%20employees%20ask%20for%20better%20pay.%20More%20money%20may%20be%20coming%20in%20the%20door%2C%20but%20it's%20going%20out%20just%20as%20quickly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20a%20challenge%20to%20maintain%20your%20prices%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20maintain%20your%20quality%2C%20not%20to%20lose%20your%20personnel%20who%20have%20helped%20to%20make%20it%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Darren%20Tristano%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Foodservice%20Results%2C%20a%20food-industry%20consultancy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJoe%20Carroll%2C%20a%20New%20York%20restaurateur%20who%20owns%20the%20barbecue%20spot%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fettesaubbq.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFette%20Sau%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20steakhouse%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stanselm.net%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESt.%20Anselm%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20told%20me%20his%20relationships%20with%20suppliers%20haven't%20changed%20much%20as%20his%20restaurants%20have%20gotten%20more%20popular.%20But%20rent%20is%20a%20different%20story.%20The%20landlord%20for%20one%20of%20his%20restaurants%20runs%20a%20mechanic%20shop%20next%20door%2C%20and%20they%20see%20the%20lines%20down%20the%20street.%20%26quot%3BThe%20landlord%20definitely%20sees%20you're%20doing%20crazy%20business%2C%20and%20they%20want%20a%20piece%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20His%20rent%20has%20quadrupled%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%20In%20some%20respects%2C%20Carroll%20doesn't%20blame%20them%2C%20but%20he%20acknowledges%20that%20for%20some%20restaurants%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20death%20knell.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20winds%20up%20happening%20is%20everyone%20gets%20a%20little%20greedy%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20work%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BRestaurants%20operate%20a%20small%20margin%20of%20success%2C%20and%20if%20you%20go%20beyond%20that%2C%20it%20becomes%20impossible%20to%20really%20succeed%20anymore%20and%20maintain%20the%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%202014%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2014%2F07%2F03%2Fopinion%2Fdanny-meyers-union-square-cafe-is-a-casualty-of-rising-rents.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20op-ed%2C%20the%20New%20York%20restaurateur%20Danny%20Meyer%20lamented%20having%20to%20move%20his%20award-winning%20Union%20Square%20Cafe%20away%20from%20its%20original%20location%20because%20of%20a%20huge%20rent%20hike.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20come%20to%20grips%20with%20the%20notion%20that%20our%20success%20has%2C%20in%20part%2C%20contributed%20to%20our%20inability%20to%20remain%20in%20our%20neighborhood%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course%2C%20there%20isn't%20a%20direct%20line%20from%20success%20to%20disaster%20in%20restaurants.%20In%20general%2C%20being%20crowded%20is%20preferable%20to%20having%20empty%20seats%2C%20and%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20adapt%20to%20newfound%20success%20is%20a%20good%20problem%20to%20have.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERyan%20Sutton%2C%20a%20New%20York-based%20food%20critic%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelotimes.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20LO%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20acknowledged%20a%20Michelin%20star%20can%20increase%20a%20restaurant's%20expenses%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20it's%20pursuing%20more%20stars%20%E2%80%94%20as%20it%20tries%20to%20continually%20serve%20the%20same%20dishes%20or%20hopes%20to%20hire%20pricier%20chefs.%20But%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20even%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-restaurants-fail-rate-2011-8%23two-years-anthos-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eif%20they%20ultimately%20failed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Michelin%20restaurants%20that%20closed%20in%20Sands'%20research%20generally%20had%20a%20pretty%20good%20run.%20%26quot%3BRestaurants%20close%20for%20so%20many%20complicated%20reasons%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Internal%20factors%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdaniels.du.edu%2Fassets%2Fresearch-hg-parsa-part-1-2015.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etend%20to%20outweigh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20external%20factors.%20If%20the%20place%20can't%20navigate%20increased%20pressure%2C%20it's%20at%20least%20in%20part%20a%20management%20issue%20because%20the%20owners%20or%20people%20running%20the%20place%20can't%20keep%20it%20together.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20to%20be%20a%20navel-gazing%20New%20Yorker%20here%2C%20but%20the%20city%20does%20have%20its%20idiosyncrasies%20that%20might%20not%20translate%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20There's%20a%20lot%20of%20tourism%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20business%20people%20and%20gatherings%20with%20big%20expense%20accounts%2C%20and%20prices%20are%20wildly%20high.%20It's%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chefspencil.com%2Fcities-with-the-most-michelin-restaurants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eone%20of%20the%20most%20Michelin-starred%20restaurant%20cities%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20world.%20As%20John%20Gordon%2C%20a%20restaurant%20analyst%20in%20San%20Diego%2C%20put%20it%20to%20me%2C%20New%20York%20City%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20rent%20is%20%26quot%3Bjust%20astronomical.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECarroll%20has%20had%20one%20Michelin-starred%20restaurant%2C%20Semilla%2C%20that%20did%2C%20indeed%2C%20close%20down.%20It%20did%20%26quot%3Bkiller%20business%26quot%3B%20for%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20after%20getting%20the%20accolade%20and%20then%20fell%20off.%20He%20doesn't%20think%20the%20star%20was%20really%20the%20problem%2C%20though.%20Semilla%20offered%20a%2010-course%20menu%20that%20didn't%20necessarily%20attract%20repeat%20business.%20%26quot%3BAnyone%20who%20needed%20to%20go%20went%2C%20and%20not%20many%20people%20were%20coming%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20%26quot%3Bcantankerous%26quot%3B%20chef%20who%20oversaw%20the%20restaurant%20was%20tough%2C%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20many%20ways%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20to%20do%20about%20growth%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20classic%20question%20in%20any%20business%2C%20including%20restaurants%20and%20hospitality.%20Do%20you%20build%20another%20location%3F%20Do%20you%20move%20to%20a%20new%2C%20bigger%20space%3F%20How%20do%20you%20manage%20supply%20chains%2C%20employee%20raise%20requests%2C%20and%20rising%20rent%20costs%3F%20How%20do%20you%20evolve%20enough%20to%20meet%20the%20moment%20without%20changing%20what%20made%20things%20work%20in%20the%20first%20place%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20successful%20restaurant%20goes%20under%2C%20there's%20usually%20some%20underlying%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Carroll%20said.%20It%20might%20be%20mismanagement%2C%20or%20the%20owner%20or%20operator%20has%20a%20personal%20problem%2C%20such%20as%20a%20drug%20addiction%2C%20or%20there's%20a%20conflict%20with%20the%20landlord.%20Some%20of%20it%20is%20within%20a%20restaurant's%20control%2C%20but%20some%20of%20it%20isn't.%20And%20even%20if%20it%20is%20within%20the%20place's%20control%2C%20it's%20a%20hard%20business%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20no%20guarantee%20that%20a%20second%20location%20in%20Philadelphia%20will%20perform%20as%20well%20as%20the%20original%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20consumer%20end%20of%20things%2C%20the%20experience%20can%20be%20frustrating%2C%20too.%20People%20want%20their%20favorite%20places%20to%20survive%20and%20thrive%20%E2%80%94%20your%20favorite%20restaurant%20is%20no%20good%20to%20you%20if%20it%20closes.%20But%20they%20also%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20keep%20frequenting%20the%20places%20they%20like%20%E2%80%94%20your%20favorite%20restaurant%20is%20no%20good%20to%20you%20if%20you%20can't%20get%20a%20reservation%20anymore.%20And%20just%20because%20a%20spot%20is%20hot%20for%20a%20minute%20doesn't%20mean%20it%20will%20stay%20that%20way%20forever.%20A%20place%20needs%20those%20regulars%20for%20a%20rainy%20Tuesday%20in%20February%20when%20the%20tourists%20wouldn't%20dare%20venture%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20understandable%20to%20want%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest.%26quot%3B%20It's%20why%20people%20spend%20hours%20curating%20their%20vacations%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20have%20the%20optimal%20trip.%20But%20if%20we%20all%20seek%20out%20the%20best%20collectively%20and%20wind%20up%20coming%20to%20the%20same%20conclusions%2C%20we%20make%20each%20other%20a%20little%20miserable.%20A%20lot%20of%20Instagram-inspired%20and%20Instagram-optimized%20trips%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fthe-goods%2F23388038%2Fpositano-travel-instagram%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewind%20up%20sucking%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20There's%20only%20so%20much%20room%20at%20the%20top%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20the%20machine%20ends%20up%20eating%20a%20great%20thing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20a%20more%20local%20level%2C%20if%20and%20when%20your%20regular%20date%20spot%20picks%20up%20a%20Michelin%20star%2C%20or%20takes%20off%20with%20the%20TikTok%20crowd%2C%20or%20lands%20on%20a%20best-of%20list%2C%20know%20it%20might%20be%20a%20minute%20before%20you%20can%20get%20a%20table.%20But%20you%20probably%20want%20to%20get%20yourself%20on%20the%20list%2C%20even%20if%20your%20reservation%20is%20six%20months%20from%20now%2C%20because%20the%20place's%20landlord%20is%20looking%20at%20the%20lease%20and%20wondering%20how%20fast%20they%20can%20start%20charging%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frestaurants-awards-michelin-star-new-york-city-dining-rent-costs-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729677361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6717df079b3250dbbce93269%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frestaurants-awards-michelin-star-new-york-city-dining-rent-costs-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20research%20shows%20restaurants%20that%20won%20major%20awards%20like%20a%20Michelin%20star%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20close%20due%20to%20the%20pressure%20of%20high%20demand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22estewart%40insider.com%20(Emily%20Stewart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%