es%20and%20sectors%2C%20instead%20of%20having%20your%20whole%20portfolio%20in%2C%20say%2C%20a%20few%20tech%20stocks.%20A%20simple%20way%20of%20doing%20that%20could%20also%20be%20putting%20money%20into%20an%20index%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20set%20up%20%3Cstrong%3Estop-loss%20orders%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20This%20can%20be%20done%20in%20a%20brokerage%20account%2C%20and%20your%20position%20is%20sold%20if%20a%20share%20price%20falls%20to%20a%20certain%20point.%20There's%20also%20the%20trailing%20stop-loss%20order%2C%20Roberts%20said%2C%20which%20adjusts%20based%20on%20upward%20movements%20in%20a%20stock's%20price.%20So%20a%205%25%20stop-loss%20limit%2C%20for%20example%2C%20moves%20up%20to%20correspond%20to%20a%20level%205%25%20below%20a%20stock's%20rising%20price%2C%20but%20will%20never%20dip%20below%20the%20original%20stop-loss%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20safeguard%20ensures%20that%20you%20are%20not%20solely%20reliant%20on%20timing%20the%20market%2C%20which%2C%20as%20we%20all%20know%2C%20is%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20do%20consistently%2C%26quot%3B%20Roberts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20third%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Etake%20profits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20on%20gains.%20With%20Nvidia%20and%20other%20AI%20stocks%20delivering%20ungodly%20returns%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20this%20piece%20of%20advice%20might%20be%20good%20for%20investors%20in%20those%20firms%20to%20hear.%20It%20can%20be%20tempting%20to%20stay%20fully%20in%20a%20stock%20that%20has%20treated%20you%20well.%20But%20doing%20so%20may%20also%20melt%20away%20the%20wealth%20you've%20built%20if%20the%20stock%20has%20a%20sudden%20turnaround%2C%20Roberts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20an%20uncommon%20issue%20that%20I%20always%20see%20with%20clients%20and%20prospects%2C%26quot%3B%20Roberts%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BGreed%20comes%20in%20three%20destructive%20forms%3A%201)%20the%20need%20to%20make%20more%2C%202)%20the%20lack%20of%20knowing%20when%20%26quot%3Benough%20is%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20and%203)%20the%20unwillingness%20to%20pay%20taxes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20suggested%20a%20strategy%20resembling%20something%20like%20taking%20half%20of%20your%20gains%20and%20buying%20safer%20assets%20like%20Treasurys%2C%20and%20said%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20paying%20taxes%20on%20capital%20gains%20can%20be%20cheaper%20than%20suffering%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20investors%2C%20it's%20crucial%20to%20understand%20that%20market%20gains%20are%20never%20guaranteed%20and%20that%20the%20risks%20of%20overexposure%20can%20be%20devastating%2C%26quot%3B%20Roberts%20said.%20If%20you're%20%26quot%3Briding%20the%20wave%20of%20massive%20market%20gains%2C%20ask%20yourself%3A%20Is%20now%20the%20time%20to%20take%20some%20chips%20off%20the%20table%3F%20Are%20your%20investments%20aligned%20with%20your%20long-term%20goals%20and%20risk%20tolerance%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-investing-strategy-downside-risk-prevent-losses-bessembinder-roberts-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729675802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6717febf01ea6d83dee33f6f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-investing-strategy-downside-risk-prevent-losses-bessembinder-roberts-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20long-term%20outperformance%20of%20major%20indexes%20like%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20most%20stocks%20lose%20value.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-investing-strategy-downside-risk-prevent-losses-bessembinder-roberts-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22John%20Turturro%2C%20Melissa%20Leo%2C%20%E2%80%9924%E2%80%99s%20Evan%20Ka