li%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20is%20hosting%20a%20major%20summit%20with%20over%2020%20world%20leaders%2C%20whom%20he's%20trying%20to%20convince%20to%20ditch%20the%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDe-dollarization%20is%20one%20of%20Putin's%20priorities%20because%20trading%20in%20local%20currencies%20means%20that%20a%20heavily%20sanctioned%20Russia%20would%20not%20be%20beholden%20to%20the%20Western%20US%20dollar-dominated%20global%20financial%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20easy%20to%20move%20away%20from%20the%20greenback.%20BRICS'%20summit%20organizers%20have%20advised%20foreign%20attendees%20to%20bring%20cash%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%2C%20US%20dollars%20and%20euros%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20event%2C%20in%20the%20Russian%20city%20of%20Kazan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20Russian%20banks%20will%20only%20take%20US%20dollars%20or%20euros%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Moscow%20has%20deemed%20%26quot%3Btoxic%20currencies%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20to%20exchange%20for%20rubles%2C%20according%20to%20a%20guide%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbrics-russia2024.ru%2Fen%2Fsummit%2Fparticipants%2Fcards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esummit's%20website.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20cashless%20isn't%20an%20option%2C%20since%20it's%20not%20possible%20to%20use%20Mastercard%20or%20Visa%20cards%20issued%20outside%20Russia%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20two%20card%20issuers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisa-mastercard-suspend-operations-in-russia-amid-ukraine-invasion-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehalted%20local%20operations%3C%2Fa%3E%20days%20after%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20Union%20Pay%20cards%20may%20be%20used%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bbut%20with%20restrictions%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttendees%20may%20apply%20for%20Russia's%20Mir%20payment%20card%20%E2%80%94%20and%20there's%20a%20bank%20at%20Kazan's%20international%20airpo