nd-microsoft-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunveiled%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20plan%20to%20lead%20a%20%24500%20million%20funding%20round%20to%20develop%20small%20modular%20nuclear%20reactors%2C%20following%20an%20earlier%20announcement%20to%20purchase%20a%20nuclear%20power%20plant%20in%20rural%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20like%20mosquitoes%20to%20light%20%E2%80%94%20we%20are%20attracted%20to%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20people%20familiar%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company's%20data%20center%20expansion%20strategy%20considers%20several%20factors%2C%20including%20system%20resiliency%20and%20latency%2C%20the%20availability%20of%20renewable%20energy%2C%20and%20the%20local%20government's%20long-term%20commitment.%20Amazon%20is%20also%20constantly%20seeking%20ways%20to%20make%20its%20data%20centers%20more%20energy%20efficient%20by%20using%20carbon-free%20resources%2C%20in-house%20processors%2C%20and%20natural%20air%20cooling%20systems%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282c2fbef-48d1-4af8-8635-cf74ee12697d%5C%22%3EHigher%20costs%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20Amazon%20is%20paying%20higher%20prices%20to%20get%20its%20new%20data%20centers%20up%20and%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20example%20is%20an%20Amazon%20facility%20in%20Santa%20Clara%2C%20California%2C%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Silicon%20Valley.%20For%20the%20last%202%20years%2C%20Amazon%20has%20held%20talks%20with%20the%20city%20of%20Santa%20Clara%20to%20secure%20power%20for%20a%20new%20data%20center%20located%20near%20Levi's%20Stadium%2C%20the%20home%20of%20the%20San%20Francisco%2049ers%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsantaclara.granicus.com%2Fplayer%2Fclip%2F2140%3Fview_id%3D1%26meta_id%3D190407%26redirect%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecity%20council%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20held%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20is%20in%20talks%20for%20a%2015-year%2C%2020-megawatt%20proposal%20for%20this%20facility%20under%20the%20condition%20that%20the%20company%20pays%20the%20full%20cost%20of%20the%20energy%2C%20whether%20it%20uses%20the%20power%20or%20not%2C%20Manuel%20Pineda%2C%20the%20chief%20electric%20utility%20officer%20of%20the%20City%20of%20Santa%20Clara%2C%20said%20during%20the%20meeting.%20Amazon%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20up%20to%2050%25%20higher%20rates%20than%20normal%20and%20will%20be%20entitled%20to%20additional%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20assurances%26quot%3B%20to%20cover%20any%20contractual%20risks%2C%20Pineda%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20Amazon%20also%20plans%20to%20use%20the%2020-megawatt%20power%20agreement%20for%20a%20second%20building%20on-site%2C%20which%20currently%20has%20no%20electric%20capacity%2C%20according%20to%20Pineda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20this%20arrangement%20has%20not%20been%20finalized%2C%20and%20the%20project%20is%20progressing%20as%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221056%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AWS%20Santa%20Clara%20data%20center%20planning%20slide%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6712fb33a0a0cc14f22269ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22586%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresentation%20slide%20from%20Santa%20Clara's%20city%20council%20meeting%3Cp%3ECity%20of%20Santa%20Clara%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e7acce5-2a9c-4e0c-873a-74b683e1b0a3%5C%22%3EAmazon%20escalates%20Santa%20Clara%20delays%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20appears%20to%20be%20dealing%20with%20further%20delays%20in%20Santa%20Clara.%20On%20August%2028%2C%20an%20AWS%20employee%20wrote%20to%20a%20city%20official%20about%20another%20facility%2C%20a%20former%20Owens%20Corning%20factory%20the%20company%20purchased%20in%202023.%20The%20email%20discussed%20delays%20at%20the%20site%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20problems%20are%20raising%20concerns%20internally%20at%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelays%20as%20significant%20as%20this%20unfortunately%20impact%20our%20ability%20to%20serve%20our%20customers%20which%20has%20resulted%20in%20escalation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20email%2C%20which%20was%20obtained%20by%20BI%20through%20a%20public-records%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20another%20Amazon%20employee%20wrote%20to%20a%20Santa%20Clara%20city%20official.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20time%20sensitive%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20staffer%20said.%20%26quot%3BAWS%20executives%20are%20highly%20concerned%20about%20the%20constant%20push%20in%20the%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a5ae3cc3-4484-42c7-a232-b1135b2bd3e0%5C%22%3E'Straining'%20water%20infrastructure%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20problem%20is%20water%20supply.%20A%20growing%20number%20of%20data%20centers%20rely%20on%20water%20instead%20of%20air%20to%20cool%20the%20servers%20and%20other%20equipment%20inside%20the%20facilities.%20This%20liquid-cooling%20technology%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farizona-running-out-of-water-data-centers-blame-microsoft-google-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erequires%20a%20lot%20of%20water%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20is%20%26quot%3Bstraining%20local%20jurisdictions'%20existing%20infrastructure%26quot%3B%20for%20water%20in%20some%20regions%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Bdependent%20on%20long-term%20infrastructure%20upgrades%20or%20building%20our%20own%20solutions%26quot%3B%20to%20mitigate%20the%20issue%2C%20the%20internal%20document%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20zoning%20and%20permitting%20problems%2C%20too.%20Some%20local%20jurisdictions%20are%20not%20supporting%20the%20re-zoning%20of%20industrial%20property%20for%20data%20center%20use%20and%20have%20stricter%20environmental%20regulations%2C%20the%20document%20explained.%20Amazon%20is%20%26quot%3Bworking%20proactively%26quot%3B%20with%20local%20municipalities%20to%20solve%20these%20challenges%2C%20as%20they%20can%20impact%20its%20%26quot%3Bfuture%20capacity%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20water%20efficient%20operators%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20data%20centers%20are%20much%20more%20water%20efficient%20than%20the%20industry%20average%2C%20the%20company's%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274b62895-25bd-411f-8890-035613989c55%5C%22%3E'Lack%20of%20available%20skilled%20labor'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20even%20bigger%20problem%20may%20be%20a%20lack%20of%20skilled%20electricians%20to%20build%20and%20run%20these%20data%20centers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20internal%20document%20and%20people%20directly%20involved%20in%20these%20Amazon%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElectrical%20work%20is%20a%20major%20part%20of%20data%20center%20construction.%20But%20Amazon%20has%20struggled%20to%20find%20enough%20people%20to%20do%20the%20jobs%2C%20especially%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20these%20people%20said.%20Amazon%20has%20talked%20to%20local%20colleges%2C%20general%20contractors%2C%20and%20labor%20unions%20in%20certain%20markets%20to%20increase%20the%20supply%20of%20electricians%2C%20one%20of%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22amazon%20data%20center%20oregon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F56269dc1dd0895726f8b45b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Amazon%20data%20center%20in%20Oregon%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F07%2F27%2Famericas-demand-skilled-electricians-boom.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshortage%20of%20skilled%20electricians%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20growing%20industry%20problem.%20According%20to%20last%20year's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatacenter.uptimeinstitute.com%2Frs%2F711-RIA-145%2Fimages%2F2023StaffingSurvey.Re