20shows%20different%20videos%20on%20motherhood.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6716c92a9b3250dbbce9098c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Soula%20app%20has%20daily%20check-in%20activities%20for%20the%20mother.%3Cp%3ESoula%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Soula%20app%20has%20an%20AI%20chatbot%2C%20Dua%2C%20that%20aids%20mothers%20with%20postpartum%20depression%20support.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20chatbots%20like%20Dua%20aim%20to%20reduce%20healthcare%20burdens%20and%20improve%20mental%20health%20access.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOB%2FGYN%20experts%20said%20that%20they%20welcome%20innovation%20in%20AI%20to%20destigmatize%20questions%20about%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECaring%20for%20a%20month-old%20newborn%20and%20two-year-old%20son%20felt%20overwhelming%20for%20LeRonika%20Francis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20first%20postpartum%20period%2C%20Francis%20said%20she%20experienced%20a%20heavy%20wave%20of%20depression%20while%20dealing%20with%20a%20baby%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fparenting%2Fwhy-is-my-newborn-crying%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecolic%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20ultimately%20sought%20the%20help%20of%20a%20counselor.%20It%20was%20not%20until%20her%20most%20recent%20pregnancy%20that%20she%20also%20started%20to%20use%20an%20AI%20chatbot%20on%20the%20fem-tech%20app%20Soula%2C%20which%20she%20said%20helped%20with%20reducing%20depressive%20symptoms%20and%20reassuring%20her%20about%20her%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20tells%20me%3A%20'Welcome%20back%2C%20LeRonika.%20Your%20reactions%20are%20natural%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Francis%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20New%20Iberia%2C%20Louisiana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20chatbot%20called%20%26quot%3BDua%26quot%3B%20also%20sent%20her%20some%20videos%20that%20she%20could%20watch%20about%20self-hugging%2C%20a%20practice%20that%20could%20reduce%20stress%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20Dua%20is%20there%20more%20than%20anything.%20It%20really%20showed%20me%3A%20OK%2C%20this%20is%20what%20you%20could%20do.%20Make%20sure%20you%20make%20time%20for%20yourself%2C%20too%2C%20because%20that's%20important%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Francis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoula%20was%20co-founded%20by%20Natallia%20Miranchuk%20and%20Andrei%20Kulik%2C%20who%20conceptualized%20a%2024%2F7%20AI%20doula%20that%20could%20close%20the%20gap%20in%20mental%20health%20support%20for%20mothers%20during%20pregnancy%20and%20postpartum%20periods.%20Rather%20than%20replacing%20medical%20providers%2C%20apps%20such%20as%20Soula%20aim%20to%20increase%20broader%20access%20to%20maternal%20healthcare.%20Healthcare%20providers%20said%20that%20these%20apps%20could%20also%20help%20reduce%20the%20burden%20on%20the%20healthcare%20system%2C%20where%20wait%20times%20can%20be%20long%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-nurses-strike-labor-union-staffing-shortage-covid-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworkers%20face%20burnout%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20OB%2FGYN%20doctors%20and%20doulas%2C%20who%20largely%20welcomed%20the%20rise%20in%20AI%20chatbots%20because%20they%20can%20make%20information%20more%20accessible%20to%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20obtained%20from%20Sensor%20Tower%2C%20Soula%20now%20has%20more%20than%2035%2C000%20downloads.%20The%20startup%20has%20fundraised%20over%20%24750%2C000%20and%20is%20backed%20by%20investors%20such%20as%C2%A0Andrey%20Mikhaylyuk%2C%C2%A0the%20former%20vice%20president%C2%A0of%20product%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funicorn-pitch-deck-flo-health-raises-200-million-series-c-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFlo%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20period%20tracking%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiranchuk%20told%20BI%20that%20her%20experiences%20as%20a%20single%20mother%20of%20two%20and%20her%20work%20as%20a%20former%20maternity%20photographer%20inspired%20her%20to%20develop%20a%20supportive%20app%20for%20women.%20Initially%20conceptualized%20as%20a%20hub%20to%20connect%20doulas%20worldwide%20to%20those%20in%20need%2C%20the%20generative%20AI%20boom%20shifted%20the%20startup's%20focus%20to%20integrating%20a%20chatbot%20that%20could%20serve%20more%20populations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20are%20shy%20to%20ask%20questions%2C%20even%20in%20the%20community%2C%20because%20they%20have%20the%20feeling%20that%20maybe%20'as%20a%20mom%2C%20I%20should%20have%20known%20that%2C%20but%20I%20don't.'%20And%20she%20doesn't%20know%20where%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Miranchuk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ease%20of%20customizing%20ChatGPT%20has%20spurred%20a%20wave%20of%20new%20AI-based%20chatbots%20like%20Soula.%20According%20to%20Sensor%20Tower%2C%20the%20companion%20apps%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FCharacter.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECharacter.ai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Talkie%2C%20and%20Paradot%20have%20more%20than%2073%20million%20collective%20downloads%2C%20soaring%20more%20than%20130%25%20between%202023%20and%202024.%20%3Cspan%3EAI%20therapy%20apps%20such%20as%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwysa-mental-health-startup-raises-fresh-vc-funding-expand-coverage-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWysa%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3EWoebot%20received%20over%201%20million%20downloads%2C%20the%20data%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorenia%20Smith%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Birth%20Justice%20Collaborative%20in%20Minnesota%2C%20said%20that%20while%20popularizing%20tools%20like%20chatbots%20can%20help%20broaden%20healthcare%20access%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20avoid%20a%20%26quot%3Bone%20size%20fits%20all%26quot%3B%20and%20ensure%20that%20AI%20can%20reflect%20the%20communities%20it%20serves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20cultural%20practices%20that%20exist%20and%20have%20existed%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%20that%20people%20still%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20human%20could%20talk%20about%20all%20their%20experience%20and%20what%20they've%20seen%20and%20give%20referrals.%20When%20you%20reach%20that%20limitation%20with%20an%20AI%2C%20it%20has%20to%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20hand%20over%20care%20or%20make%20a%20referral%20in%20a%20way%20where%20people%20don't%20feel%20dropped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22245c9b56-b4a4-4a1a-abbc-5f6bbf950f49%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20role%20of%20a%20doula%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20chatbot%20Dua%20aims%20to%20function%20like%20a%20doula%2C%20providing%20mothers%20with%20information%20about%20the%20pregnancy%20experience%20during%20a%20time%20of%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoulas%20are%20trained%20professionals%20who%20can%20provide%20non-medical%2C%20continuous%20physical%2C%20emotional%2C%20and%20information%20support%20for%20women%20before%2C%20during%2C%20and%20after%20childbirth%2C%20helping%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC10292163%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduce%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0mental%20health-related%20morbidity%20for%20the%20mother%20and%20reduce%20infant%20mortality%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccess%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fwhat-is-a-doula%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoulas%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20costly.%20While%20there's%20Medicaid%20coverage%20for%20doulas%20in%20several%20states%2C%20not%20all%20private%20health%20insurance%20plans%20cover%20these%20expenses.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0266613821003120%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELong%20wait%20times%20and%20socioeconomic%20inequality%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20contribute%20to%20increased%20levels%20of%20stress%20and%20lack%20of%20healthcare%20usage%20among%20mothers%20and%20pregnant%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTraditionally%2C%20it's%20been%20something%20that's%20been%20available%20only%20to%20folks%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20resources.%20The%20people%20that%20benefit%20the%20most%20from%20doula%20care%20are%20those%20that%20might%20not%20trust%20the%20healthcare%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr.%20Devon%20Rupley%2C%20an%20attending%20physician%20and%20OB%2FGYN%20specialist%20at%20NYC%20Health.%20%26quot%3BThat%20tends%20to%20be%20people%20of%20color%20who've%20had%20previously%20negative%20experiences%20with%20racism%20and%20bias%20that%20can%20really%20harm%20their%20experience%20in%20the%20healthcare%20system%20generally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERupley%20added%20that%20using%20an%20AI%20healthcare%20app%20to%20address%20basic%20questions%20can%20allow%20patients%20to%20spend%20higher-quality%20time%20with%20doctors%20by%20asking%20high-level%20questions%20and%20discussing%20their%20healthcare%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dua%2C%20an%20AI%20chatbot%2C%20talks%20to%20the%20user%20with%20texts.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6716cbe801ea6d83dee30651%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDua%20is%20the%20Soula%20app's%20built-in%20AI%20chatbot.%3Cp%3ESoula%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b015d0f-002f-4d99-8f8d-2ae73851d6bc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20design%20an%20empathetic%20AI%20chatbot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESoula%20enlisted%20real-life%20doulas%20to%20help%20train%20its%20chatbot%20and%20strike%20the%20right%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20create%20it%20to%20be%20as%20personable%20as%20talking%20to%20a%20real-life%20person%2C%20but%20we%20can%20try%20to%20create%20that%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lexi%20Pacheco%2C%20a%20doula%20from%20Arizona%20who%20worked%20to%20help%20refine%20the%20dialogue%20in%20Soula's%20chatbot%20Dua.%20For%20%2422%20per%20hour%2C%20she%20helped%20improve%20the%20chatbot%20by%20using%20it%20%26quot%3Bhand-in-hand%26quot%3B%20during%20her%20pregnancies%2C%20adding%20in%20her%20expertise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20asking%20questions%20on%20Google%20could%20yield%20more%20informational%20responses%2C%20Pacheco%20said%20mothers%20would%20want%20something%20that%20provided%20%26quot%3Bmore%20of%20that%20reassurance%20that%20Google%20wouldn't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Armani%20Grant%2C%20a%20Soula%20user%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewho%20became%20pregnant%20at%2018%2C%20Google%20felt%20overwhelming.%20The%20chatbot%20allowed%20her%20to%20ask%20questions%20that%20she%20wouldn't%20feel%20comfortable%20asking%20her%20mother.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPacheco%20said%20many%20women%20she's%20worked%20with%20reported%20similar%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20might%20even%20feel%20incompetent%20to%20ask%20the%20question%2C%20which%20no%20woman%20should%20ever%20feel%2C%20but%20with%20my%20history%20of%20working%20with%20people%2C%20they%20definitely%20tend%20to%20revert%20to%3A%20I'm%20sorry%2C%20I'm%20asking%20this%20question%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20and%20that%20might%20just%20be%20because%20of%20the%20societal%20pressure%20that%20more%20medicalized%20doctors%20have%20put%20on%20people%20that%20they%20don't%20give%20the%20time%20and%20day%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Pacheco%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20isn't%20meant%20to%20completely%20replace%20a%20doula.%20Moreover%2C%20retention%20rates%20of%20AI%20healthcare%20chatbots%20can%20be%20low%2C%20said%20Johannes%20Eichstaedt%2C%20a%20computational%20social%20scientist%20and%20assistant%20professor%20of%20psychology%20at%20Stanford%20University.%20The%20high%20dropout%20rates%20for%20healthcare%20apps%20are%20%26quot%3Ban%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Pacheco%20said%20AI%20bots%20can%20help%20%26quot%3Bcalm%20nerves%26quot%3B%20and%20fill%20the%20gaps%20when%20patients%20feel%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bbothering%26quot%3B%20their%20healthcare%20providers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20isn't%20like%20a%20healthcare%20provider%20to%20give%20you%20guidance%2C%20but%20it's%20supposed%20to%20be%20there%20to%20give%20you%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20comfort%2C%26quot%3B%20Pacheco%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoula-ai-chatbot-postpartum-healthcare-gap-women-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729674001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67181b8301ea6d83dee34cfb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoula-ai-chatbot-postpartum-healthcare-gap-women-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Soula%20app%20users%20and%20OB%2FGYB%20experts%20spoke%20about%20the%20role%20that%20AI%20chatbots%20can%20have%20in%20healthcare%20access.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hli%40businessinsider.com%20(Helen%20Li)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoula-ai-chatbot-postpartum-healthcare-gap-women-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Varun%20reveals%20what%20Atlee%20says%20about%20Samantha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729673641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114500451%2Cimgsize-25244.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fcitadel-honey-bunny-varun-dhawan-reveals-what-atlee-says-about-samantha-ruth-prabhu%2Farticleshow%2F114500483.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F114500483.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%221