3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20grilled%20the%20central%20-%20and%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20-%20governments%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20arguments%20over%20states'%20non-compliance%20with%2C%20and%20failure%20to%20enforce%2C%20anti-pollution%20measures%2C%20rolled%20into%20yet%20another%20hearing%2C%20even%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-aqi-anti-pollution-plan-on-delhi-air-quality-remains-very-poor-6852128%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair%20quality%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20national%20capital%20region%20remains%20'very%20poor'%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20prompts%20concern%20over%20the%20risk%20of%20increased%20respiratory%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%2C%20Justice%20A%20Amanullah%2C%20and%20Justice%20AG%20Masih%2C%20dismissed%20as%20%26quot%3Bmere%20eyewash%26quot%3B%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20governments'%20efforts%20to%20stamp%20out%20farm%20fires%20-%20i.e.%2C%20farmers%20burning%20agricultural%20waste%20-%20that%20contribute%20to%20toxic%20air%20smothering%20Delhi%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20governments%20were%20questioned%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20prosecution%2C%20or%20even%20imposition%20of%20commensurate%20financial%20penalties%2C%20of%20farmers%20violating%20the%20law%2C%20and%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Haryana%2C%20even%20suggested%20the%20failure%20to%20enforce%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolicy%20devised%20by%20you%26quot%3B%20to%20favour%20some%20farmers%20over%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20rapped%20the%20union%20government%20over%20%26quot%3Btoothless%26quot%3B%20environmental%20protection%20laws%2C%20observing%20that%20laws%20meant%20to%20control%20pollution%2C%20specifically%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%20Act%20of%202021%C2%A0had%20been%20passed%20sans%20the%20administrative%20machinery%20to%20ensure%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20Section%2015%20of%20the%20Environmental%20Protection%20Act%20-%20which%20covers%20penalties%20for%20violating%20anti-pollution%20laws%20-%20had%20amended%20so%20%26quot%3Bprocedure%20for%20imposing%20penalty%20cannot%20be%20followed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%2015%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bonly%20section%20for%20enforcing%20the%20EPA%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20was%20pointed%20out%2C%20to%20which%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20centre%2C%20said%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bfully%20operationalised%26quot%3B%20in%2010%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BNot%20A%20Single%20Prosecution...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20was%20the%20first%20to%20feel%20the%20court's%20wrath%2C%20with%20Justice%20Oka%20doubting%20its%20claim%20that%2044%20people%20had%20been%20prosecuted.%20%26quot%3BYour%20Advocate-General%20said%20nothing%20was%20done...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20told%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Punjab%20government%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20not%20a%20single%20prosecution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20told%20that%20Rs%2011%20lakh%20had%20been%20recovered%2C%20as%20fines%2C%20from%20417%20people%20violating%20the%20stubble%20burning%20laws%2C%20but%20declared%20itself%20unhappy%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bnominal%26quot%3B%20amounts%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgiving-you-1-week-supreme-court-rebukes-punjab-haryana-over-delhi-air-pollution-6800324%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BPunjab%20Should%20Say%20It%20Is%20Helpless%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20On%20Delhi%20Air%20Pollution%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20impose%20nominal%20fines...%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Oka%20observed%20when%20told%20fines%20varied%20from%20Rs%202%2C500%20to%20Rs%205%2C000%20per%20violator.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20given%20licence%20to%20people%20(to%20commit%20the%20crime)%20...%26quot%3B%20he%20noted%2C%20also%20asking%20Mr%20Singhvi%20why%20684%20others%20violating%20the%20same%20law%20had%20been%20spared%20any%20penalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Punjab%20government's%20Chief%20Secretary%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3Bvery%20small%20fires%26quot%3B%20were%20sometimes%20overlooked%2C%20to%20which%20the%20court%20responded%20sharply%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20minimum%20expected%20of%20you%20is%20to%20fine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaryana%20Govt%20'Under%20Fire'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20moved%20to%20the%20Haryana%20government%2C%20and%20lamented%20that%20not%20one%20prosecution%20had%20been%20recorded%20since%20June%202021%2C%20when%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%2C%20a%20central%20government%20panel%2C%20issued%20orders%20to%20prosecute%20those%20violating%20the%20anti-farm%20fires%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20claimed%20success%20in%20controlling%20farm%20fires%2C%20pointing%20to%20data%20that%20claims%20only%20655%20had%20been%20reported%20this%20year%20(of%20which%20around%20200%20were%20found%20to%20be%20false%20flags)%20compared%20to%20nearly%2010%2C000%20earlier%2C%20but%20the%20court%20was%20not%20fully%20convinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(If)%20there%20are%20around%20400%20fires%20why%20have%20only%2032%20police%20cases%20been%20filed%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOthers%20have%20been%20penalised%20as%20per%20Section%2015%20of%20EPA...%20we%20have%20collected%20Rs%202%20crore%20totally%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20state%20government%20responded%2C%20to%20which%20a%20cynical%20court%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20collecting%20under%20Section%2015%20so%20they%20can%20be%20later%20quashed%20(and%20amount%20returned%20to%20farmers)%20on%20appeal%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20Chief%20Secretary%20sought%20credit%20for%20having%20reduced%20the%20count%20of%20farm%20fires%20but%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20entirely%20unhappy%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20all%20hogwash...%20Is%20this%20some%20policy%20devised%20by%20you%3F%20So%2C%20some%20people%20are%20arrested%2C%20and%20some%20others%20just%20fined%3F%20We%20are%20very%20sceptical...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20cast%20doubt%20over%20the%20drastic%20reduction%20in%20farm%20fire%20numbers%2C%20suggesting%20that%20many%20may%20not%20have%20been%20recorded.%20%26quot%3BAgain...%20in%20some%2C%20police%20cases%20are%20registered%2C%20and%20in%20others%20there%20is%20nominal%20amount%20(of%20fine%20recovered).%20There%20needs%20to%20be%20consistency%20in%20the%20approach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BStates%20Interested%20In%20Implementing%20Law%26quot%3B%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20%26quot%3Bthere%20will%20have%20been%20at%20least%20one%20prosecution...%20if%20(Punjab%20and%20Haryana)%20are%20really%20interested%20in%20implementing%20the%20law%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20wondered%20aloud%20about%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20reasons%26quot%3B%20for%20that%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20it%20was%20submitted%20that%20sometimes%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20reasons%26quot%3B%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20take%20action%3B%20Justice%20Oka%20had%20then%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20political%20issue...%20it%20is%20about%20implementation%20of%20statutory%20directions...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20warned%20officials%20from%20CAQM%20-%20which%20it%20last%20week%20slammed%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btoothless%20wonder%26quot%3B%20for%20failing%20to%20enforce%20its%20orders%20and%20questioned%20its%20members'%20competence%20-%20it%20would%20take%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20irate%20court%20trained%20its%20guns%20on%20the%20anti-pollution%20panel%20today%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20winter%20approaches%20Delhi%20and%20the%20NCR%20air%20quality%20levels%20usual