%9CManayek%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%2020-episode%20affair%20from%20Yoav%20Gross%20Productions%2C%20has%20sold%20its%20second%20and%20third%20seasons%20to%20France%20and%20Germany.%20The%20thriller%20follows%20a%20veteran%20internal%20affairs%20investigator%20who%20stumbles%20across%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20police%20corruption%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22K.J.%20Yossman%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Fcineflix-rights-manayek-the-minister-europe-australia-sales-1236184517%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAbetting%20Crime%26quot%3B%3A%20Centre%20Blasts%20'X'%20After%20100%20Flight%20Bomb%20Threats%20In%20A%20Week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20barrage%20of%20bomb%20threats%20received%20by%20airlines%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%2C%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20IT%20today%20blasted%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20through%20which%20many%20of%20these%20hoaxes%20were%20circulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoint%20Secretary%20Sanket%20S%20Bhondve%20chaired%20a%20virtual%20meeting%20with%20representatives%20of%20airlines%20and%20social%20media%20platforms%20such%20as%20X%20and%20Meta.%20The%20official%20said%20that%20the%20situation%20amounts%20to%20%26quot%3BX%20abetting%20crime%26quot%3B%20and%20questioned%20its%20representatives%20on%20the%20steps%20taken%20to%20stop%20such%20alarming%20rumours%20from%20spreading%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20120%20flights%20operated%20by%20Indian%20carriers%20have%20received%20bomb%20threats%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days.%20Even%20yesterday%2C%2030%20flights%20operated%20by%20IndiGo%2C%20Vistara%20and%20Air%20India%20received%20such%20threats.%20The%20airlines%20said%20they%20followed%20standard%20operating%20procedures%3A%20authorities%20were%20alerted%20and%20security%20protocols%20were%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20briefing%20on%20the%20situation%20on%20Monday%2C%20Civil%20Aviation%20Minister%20K%20Rammohan%20Naidu%20said%20the%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20tackle%20it%20without%20compromising%20passengers'%20safety.%20He%20added%20that%20those%20circulating%20such%20hoax%20threats%20will%20face%20tough%20action%2C%20including%20being%20put%20on%20a%20no-fly%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20plans%20to%20amend%20the%20Suppression%20of%20Unlawful%20Acts%20against%20Safety%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20Act%20so%20that%20action%20could%20be%20initiated%20for%20offences%20when%20an%20aircraft%20is%20on%20the%20ground.%20Currently%2C%20the%20aviation%20security%20norms%20largely%20cover%20in-flight%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20amendments%20and%20the%20legal%20team%20has%20worked%20on%20it...%20We%20need%20consultations%20with%20other%20ministries%20also...%20we%20are%20definitively%20pushing%20forward%20to%20have%20changes%20in%20the%20Act%20also%20so%20that%20it%20addresses%20offences%20that%20happen%20when%20the%20flight%20is%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20also%20make%20it%20cognizable%20offence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20there%20could%20be%20a%20conspiracy%20behind%20the%20barrage%20of%20threats%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20was%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20investigation%2C%20we%20cannot%20put%20out%20any%20pattern...%20let%20us%20wait%20for%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threats%20have%20created%20panic%20among%20the%20passengers%20and%20set%20off%20alarm%20bells%20for%20security%20agencies.%20Several%20flights%2C%20including%20international%20ones%2C%20have%20been%20diverted%20after%20the%20threats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20keeping%20ourselves%20dynamic%20and%20not%20rigid...%20assessing%20and%20learning%20from%20what%20is%20happening.%20Everything%20is%20taken%20on%20a%20case-by-case%20basis.%20Based%20on%20our%20learning%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20assess%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20continuously%20talking%20to%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%20We%20are%20pushing%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20process.%20While%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20efficiently%20tackle%20the%20situation%2C%20we%20are%20not%20compromising%20on%20the%20safety%20and%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Naidu%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stressed%20that%20even%20though%20these%20were%20hoax%20threats%2C%20they%20have%20to%20be%20taken%20seriously.%20Security%20has%20been%20enhanced%20at%20airports%20and%20there%20is%20more%20checking%20at%20checkpoints.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20increased%20(the%20number%20of)%20CCTV%20cameras%20so%20that%20airports%20get%20monitored%20more%20thoroughly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729666440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fcu8hkg8o_airplane-generic_625x300_30_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fairline-bomb-threats-meity-abetting-crime-centre-blasts-x-after-100-flight-bomb-threats-in-a-week-6853613%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20barrage%20of%20bomb%20threats%20received%20by%20airlines%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%2C%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20IT%20today%20blasted%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20through%20which%20many%20of%20these%20hoaxes%20were%20circulated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chiranjeevi%2C%20Rishab%20Shetty%20wish%20Prabhas%20on%20b'day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729666380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114495487%2Cimgsize-1092454.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.i