n%20open-source%20library%20of%20templates%20that%20includes%20contracts%2C%20policies%2C%20and%20letters%20of%20intent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20issue%20that%20lawyers%20have%20is%20that%20they%20are%20always%20overworked%20and%20understaffed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rafie%20Faruq%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Genie%20AI.%20%26quot%3BOur%20software%20allows%20them%20to%20turn%20around%20a%20contract%20in%20minutes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenie%20AI's%20platform%20aims%20to%20help%20businesses%20reduce%20costs%20because%20%26quot%3Bcontracts%20are%20turned%20around%20faster%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdeals%20get%20done%20faster%2C%26quot%3B%20Faruq%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20generates%20revenue%20by%20charging%20an%20annual%20subscription%20fee%20based%20on%20usage.%20Genie%20said%20that%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20companies%20now%20use%20its%20platform%2C%20nearly%20a%20fourfold%20increase%20from%20the%2026%2C000%20listed%20on%20its%20funding%20pitch%20deck%2C%20shared%20exclusively%20with%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20excited%20by%20this%20because%20everyone%20hates%20the%20billable%20hour%20in%20law%3B%20it%20incentivizes%20working%20long%20over%20the%20value%20of%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Faruq%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20interested%20in%20flipping%20the%20business%20model%20on%20its%20head%20%E2%80%94%20can%20we%20build%20on%20value%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegal%20tech%20has%20attracted%20investor%20interest%2C%20with%20startups%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpitch-deck-legal-tech-startup-robin-ai-raise-series-b-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobin%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexclusive-legal-ai-startup-leya-raising-new-round-redpoint%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELeya%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsequoia-funding-round-legal-generative-artific