0to%20120%20kmph.%20The%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20this%20morning%20said%20that%20a%20deep%20depression%20over%20the%20east-central%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20has%20intensified%20into%20a%20cyclonic%20storm%20'Dana'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%205.30%20am%20today%2C%20the%20system%20lay%20560%20km%20southeast%20of%20Paradip%20(Odisha)%20and%20630%20km%20south-southeast%20of%20Sagar%20Island%20(West%20Bengal)%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20very%20likely%20to%20move%20in%20a%20northwestward%20direction%20and%20intensify%20further%20into%20a%20severe%20cyclonic%20storm%20over%20the%20northwest%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20by%20Thursday%20morning%2C%20the%20premier%20weather%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESubject%3A%20Cyclonic%20storm%20over%20eastcentral%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20(Cyclone%20Alert%20for%20Odisha%20and%20West%20Bengal%20coasts)%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnYesterday's%20deep%20depression%20over%20Eastcentral%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20moved%20west-northwestwards%20with%20a%20speed%20of%2018%20kmph%20during%20past%206%20hours%20intensified%20into%20a%20cyclonic%20storm%20%E2%80%9CDANA%E2%80%9D%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FerbYsIBmaw%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FerbYsIBmaw%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(%40Indiametdept)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndiametdept%2Fstatus%2F1848941110024130976%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Met%20department%20advised%20fishermen%20not%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20sea%20till%20October%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECyclone%20Dana%20Shuts%20Schools%20In%20Odisha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Odisha%2C%20all%20educational%20institutions%20including%20schools%2C%20colleges%20and%20universities%20have%20been%20shut%20in%2014%20districts%20till%20October%2025%20ahead%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcyclone-dana-expected-to-hit-odisha-and-bengal-explained-how-it-was-named-6844646%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECyclone%20Dana's%20landfall%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Charan%20Majhi-led%20Odisha%20government%20has%20cancelled%20leave%20for%20its%20employees%20and%20placed%20all%20coastal%20districts%20on%20high%20alert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Odisha%20Disaster%20Rapid%20Action%20Force%20and%20fire%20service%20personnel%20have%20also%20been%20put%20on%20standby%2C%20with%20particular%20attention%20to%20the%20districts%20of%20Kendrapara%2C%20Jagatsinghpur%2C%20Puri%2C%20Balasore%2C%20Bhadrak%2C%20Ganjam%20and%20Khorda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBengal%20Braces%20For%20Cyclone%20Dana%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20schools%20in%20seven%20districts%20will%20remain%20closed%20till%20October%2026%20in%20view%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwest-bengal-shuts-schools-icds-centres-in-9-districts-ahead-of-cyclone-6850742%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECyclone%20Dana%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20districts%20likely%20to%20be%20impacted%20most%20include%20South%2024%20Parganas%2C%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20and%20Purba%20Medinipur%2C%20along%20with%20coastal%20areas%20and%20neighbouring%20districts%20like%20Paschim%20Medinipur%2C%20Bankura%2C%20Jhargram%2C%20and%20Hooghly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20want%20to%20take%20any%20risk.%20Schools%20and%20colleges%20are%20sometimes%20used%20as%20shelters%20for%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-doctors-withdraw-hunger-strike-after-meet-with-mamata-banerjee-6841766%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMamata%20Banerjee%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%2C%20adding%20her%20government%20is%20ready%20to%20face%20the%20cyclone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20150%20express%2Fpassenger%20trains%20running%20through%20South%20Eastern%20Railway%20(SER)%20jurisdiction%20have%20been%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kolkata-headquartered%20SER%20zone%20is%20spread%20over%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trains%20cancelled%20include%20Howrah-Secunderabad%20Falaknuma%20Express%2C%20Kamakhya-Yesvantpur%20AC%20Express%2C%20Howrah-Puri%20Shatabdi%20Express%2C%20Howrah-Bhubaneswar%20Shatabdi%20Express%20and%20Howrah-Yesvantpur%20Express.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20said%20the%20trains%20cancelled%20were%20scheduled%20to%20depart%20their%20originating%20stations%20between%20October%2023%20and%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20trains%20running%20through%20the%20SER%20zone%20may%20be%20cancelled%20if%20the%20situation%20demands%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECyclone%20Dana%20Was%20Named%20By%20Qatar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20World%20Meteorological%20Organisation%20(WMO)%2C%20Cyclone%20Dana's%20name%20was%20suggested%20by%20Qatar.%20It%20means%20%26quot%3Bgenerosity%26quot%3B%20in%20Arabic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WMO%20says%20that%20assigning%20names%20to%20tropical%20cyclones%20makes%20tracking%20and%20discussing%20specific%20storms%20more%20%26quot%3Bstraightforward%2C%20especially%20when%20multiple%20storms%20are%20active%20simultaneously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNaming%20also%20helps%20to%20avoid%20confusion%20among%20meteorologists%2C%20media%2C%20emergency%20management%20agencies%20and%20the%20public.%20Additionally%2C%20naming%20tropical%20cyclones%20can%20aid%20historical%20record-keeping%20and%20research%20on%20storm%20behaviour%20and%20impacts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20WMO%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729662720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fcts7erpg_cyclone-dana_625x300_23_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcycl