have%20made%20up%20more%20than%2070%25%20of%20food%20sales%20in%20recent%20years%20in%20top%20McDonald's%20markets%2C%20an%20executive%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20underlines%20just%20how%20important%20the%20Quarter%20Pounder%20is%20to%20McDonald's%20%E2%80%94%20and%20why%20it%20will%20want%20to%20address%20the%20food-safety%20concerns%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20sense%20the%20importance%2C%20too%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmcd-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%20stock%3C%2Fa%3E%20tumbled%20sharply%20late%20Tuesday%20as%20the%20company%20said%20it%20would%20temporarily%20remove%20the%20burgers%20from%20menus%20in%20numerous%20states%20across%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Quarter%20Pounder%20is%20extremely%20important%20to%20the%20McDonald's%20product%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20A.%20Gordon%2C%20a%20chain-restaurant%20analyst%20who%20founded%20Pacific%20Management%20Consulting%20Group%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20E.%20coli%20outbreak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20a%20hit%20to%20the%20Quarter%20Pounder's%20reputation%20could%20negatively%20affect%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20and%20pose%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20McDonald's%20brand%20in%20the%20short%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20internal%20message%20published%20on%20the%20company's%20website%20Tuesday%2C%20Cesar%20Pi%C3%B1a%2C%20the%20company's%20North%20America%20chief%20supply-chain%20officer%2C%20said%20McDonald's%20was%20taking%20%26quot%3Bswift%20and%20decisive%26quot%3B%20action%20in%20response%20to%20the%20outbreak.%20Pi%C3%B1a%20said%20the%20illnesses%20might%20be%20linked%20to%20slivered%20onions%20used%20in%20the%20Quarter%20Pounder.%20He%20said%20those%20onions%20were%20sourced%20from%20a%20single%20supplier%20serving%20three%20distribution%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McDonald's%20Quarter%20Pounder%20with%20fries%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671818b0a0a0cc14f22322c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20McDonald's%20Quarter%20Pounder%20now%20uses%20fresh%20beef%20after%20its%202018%20revamp.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223a93d927-2133-4977-99a5-7756401bfdd3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevamping%20a%20McDonald's%20fan%20favorite%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthen-and-now-mcdonalds-menu-items-2020-2%23but-its-burger-offerings-havent-stopped-with-the-big-mac-the-quarter-pounder-was-released-in-1971-and-in-2007-mcdonalds-released-an-angus-third-pounder-burger-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQuarter%20Pounder%20dates%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%201971%20when%20a%20franchisee%20named%20Al%20Bernardin%20created%20the%20burger%20at%20his%20Fremont%2C%20California%2C%20store%2C%20naming%20the%20sandwich%20for%20its%20precooked%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202018%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20it%20would%20stop%20using%20frozen%20beef%20patties%20for%20its%20Quarter%20Pounders%20and%20instead%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-mcdonalds-makes-burgers-fresh-beef-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswitch%20to%20fresh%20meat%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20came%20as%20competitors%20like%20Wendy's%20were%20using%20fresh%20meat%20%E2%80%94%20and%20upstarts%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshake-shack-review-first-time-visit-burger-fries-shake-photos-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShake%20Shack%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20drawing%20customer%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20transition%20to%20a%20new%20Quarter%20Pounder%20included%20the%20addition%20of%20new%20kitchen%20utensils%20and%20refrigerators%20at%20the%20company's%20locations%20and%20an%20advertising%20campaign%20complete%20with%20a%20John%20Goodman-voiced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F271539135%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommercial%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20CEO%20Chris%20Kempczinski%2C%20then%20the%20McDonald's%20USA%20president%2C%20called%20the%20Quarter%20Pounder%20overhaul%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20significant%20change%20to%20our%20system%20and%20restaurant%20operations%20since%20All%20Day%20Breakfast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20after%20its%20release%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202019%20that%20it%20sold%2040%20million%20more%20Quarter%20Pounders%20than%20in%20the%20same%20quarter%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20doesn't%20break%20out%20sales%20figures%20for%20individual%20menu%20items%2C%20but%20presentations%20to%20investors%20in%20recent%20years%20hint%20at%20just%20how%20important%20%26quot%3Bclassics%26quot%3B%20like%20the%20Quarter%20Pounder%20and%20Big%20Mac%20are%20to%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Ian%20Borden%2C%20then%20the%20president%20of%20the%20company's%20international%20division%20%E2%80%94%20and%20now%20CFO%20of%20the%20whole%20business%20%E2%80%94%20said%20long-standing%20menu%20items%20represented%20about%2070%25%20of%20food%20sales%20in%20its%20top%20markets.%20%26quot%3BOur%20core%20classics%20are%20the%20heart%20of%20our%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Quarter%20Pounder%20is%20similarly%20important%20to%20McDonald's%20from%20a%20branding%20perspective.%20The%20Golden%20Arches%20sold%20a%20whole%20product%20line%20devoted%20to%20it%20%E2%80%94%20T-shirts%2C%20mittens%2C%20calendars%2C%20and%20other%20merch%2C%20including%20the%20%26quot%3BI'd%20Rather%20Be%20Eating%20...%20%26quot%3B%20sticker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22261cd0b3-08cf-4309-a561-292ed0b6a229%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20E.%20coli%20outbreak%20has%20killed%20one%2C%20the%20CDC%20says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CDC%20said