20to%20reflect%20how%20we%20work%2C%20not%20dictate%20how%20we%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20June%20update%2C%20Netflix%20ditched%20the%20freedom%20and%20responsibility%20section%20of%20its%20culture%20deck%20and%20added%20a%20new%20one%20called%20%26quot%3BPeople%20Over%20Process%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20focuses%20on%20hiring%20%26quot%3Bunusually%20responsible%20people%26quot%3B%20who%20thrive%20on%20openness%20and%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20added%20a%20line%20to%20its%20notorious%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-new-culture-memo-keeper-test-changes-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKeeper's%20Test%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20managers%20use%20to%20determine%20when%20it's%20time%20to%20let%20an%20employee%20go%20by%20asking%20themselves%20if%20they%20would%20fight%20to%20keep%20an%20employee%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20leave.%20The%20new%20version%20includes%20a%20disclaimer%20about%20how%20everyone%20is%20encouraged%20to%20speak%20to%20their%20managers%20regularly%20about%20what%20is%20going%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix's%20%26quot%3BKeeper's%20Test%26quot%3B%20was%20introduced%20to%20the%20public%20in%20a%20more%20than%20100-page%20memo%20published%20in%202009.%20Sarandos%20said%20Netflix%20founder%20Reed%20Hastings%20created%20the%20culture%20memo%20when%20the%20company%20had%20under%20300%20employees%20and%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bperfectly%20suited%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20company's%20needs%20at%20the%20time.%20However%2C%20Netflix%20has%20since%20grown%20its%20staff%20and%20become%20the%20largest%20streaming%20platform%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20it%20was%20one%20of%20those%20things%20where%20we%20didn't%20take%20lightly%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20document%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarandos%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20actually%20reflects%20much%20more%20today%20our%2014%2C000%20employee%20business%20culture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarandos%20said%20the%20original%20version%20probably%20placed%20a%20bit%20%26quot%3Bmore%20emphasis%20on%20freedom%20than%20responsibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20think%20you%20have%20to%20have%20both.%20So%20it's%20ways%20of%20re-crafting%20some%20of%20those%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarandos%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20core%20values%20in%20the%20new%20document%20are%20all%20in%20the%20old%20document%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%2C%20once%20referred%20to%20%3Cspan%3Eby%20former%20Meta%20COO%20Sheryl%20Sandberg%20as%20possibly%20being%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflixs-management-and-culture-presentation-2013-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20important%20document%20ever%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20valley%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%20aims%20to%20preserve%20a%20culture%20that%20attracts%20top%20talent%20and%20an%20environment%20of%20high-performers%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20previously%20updated%20the%20memo%2C%20including%20a%202022%20rewrite%20that%20exalted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-overhauled-culture-memo-reveals-streaming-company-future-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Brepresentation%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bartistic%20expression%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20keeping%20the%20document's%20focus%20on%20meritocracy.%20In%20the%202022%20update%2C%20Netflix%20suggested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-company-culture-guidelines-employees-can-quit-if-they-disagree-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemployees%20could%20quit%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20they%20didn't%20want%20to%20work%20on%20content%20they%20disagreed%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Netflix%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20In