iodiversity%2Findia-has-718-snow-leopards-most-of-them-live-in-unprotected-areas-centre-94174%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoint%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%20collaboration%20with%20other%20non-profit%20organisations%20on%2030%20January%202024%2C%20there%20are%20just%20718%20snow%20leopards%20in%20India%2C%20of%20which%20only%20a%20third%20are%20under%20legal%20protection.%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EStatus%20Report%20of%20Snow%20Leopards%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted%20that%20barely%2034%25%20of%20the%201%2C20%2C000%20square%20kilometres%20of%20snow%20leopard%20habitat%20in%20India%20is%20legally%20protected.%20Less%20than%2070%25%20of%20this%20predator%E2%80%99s%20habitat%20remains%20unprotected.%20%3Cem%3E(Above%20images%20of%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%2C%20a%20snow%20leopard%20%26amp%3B%20Charudutt%20Mishra)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20figures%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20for%20local%20communities%20to%20be%20engaged%20in%20the%20conservation%20of%20this%20threatened%20species.%20Here%20are%20eight%20conservationists%20who%20have%20done%20incredible%20work%20in%20not%20only%20understanding%20snow%20leopards%20but%20also%20engaging%20local%20communities%20to%20protect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECharudutt%20Mishra%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharudutt%20Mishra%20(Charu)%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Snow%20Leopard%20Trust%2C%20is%20considered%20by%20many%20as%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20foremost%20expert%20on%20snow%20leopard%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20a%20pioneer%20of%20the%20community-based%20conservation%20model%20and%20has%20spent%20nearly%20three%20decades%20spearheading%20groundbreaking%20projects.%20In%201997%2C%20he%20embarked%20upon%20a%20PhD%20in%20the%20remote%20village%20of%20Kibber%2C%20in%20Spiti%20Valley%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20Upon%20reaching%20there%2C%20he%20heard%20a%20disturbing%20story%20that%20a%20snow%20leopard%20had%20recently%20been%20mercilessly%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20letting%20anger%20or%20distrust%20get%20in%20the%20way%2C%20Charu%20immersed%20himself%20in%20the%20community%20and%20took%20the%20time%20to%20understand%20the%20hardships%20under%20which%20they%20lived.%20He%20learnt%20that%20local%20communities%20were%20not%20unwilling%20but%20unable%20to%20%E2%80%9Cactually%20participate%20in%20conservation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Snow%20Leopard%20(Images%20courtesy%20Karamjeet%20Singh%2FX)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-Day-Image-1729606226-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371727%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESnow%20Leopard%20(Images%20courtesy%20Karamjeet%20Singh%2FX)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkin%20to%20the%20model%20later%20adopted%20by%20the%20late%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F368687%2Fworld-animal-welfare-day-remembering-pioneers-wildlife-conservation-india-project-tiger%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERinchen%20Wangchuk%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%20of%20Snow%20Leopard%20Conservancy-India%20Trust%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20Charu%20created%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20community-managed%20livestock%20insurance%20programme%20in%202002%20%E2%80%94%20followed%20by%20other%20community-based%20conservation%20and%20livelihood%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20he%20established%20the%20Global%20Snow%20Leopard%20and%20Ecosystem%20Protection%20Programme%2C%20%E2%80%9Can%20intergovernmental%20alliance%20of%20all%2012%20snow%20leopard%20range%20countries%20working%20towards%20their%20protection%E2%80%9D.%20Today%2C%20he%20continues%20to%20impart%20valuable%20knowledge%20to%20other%20conservationists%20on%20how%20to%20ethically%20and%20effectively%20engage%20with%20local%20communities%20to%20protect%20snow%20leopards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhitleyaward.org%2Fwinners%2Fbuilding-global-capacity-for-community-led-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhitley%20Fund%20for%20Nature%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERinchen%20Wangchuk%2C%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%2C%20and%20Jigmet%20Dadul%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wildlife%20researcher%20from%20Ladakh%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246169%2Fladakh-snow-leopard-conservancy-india-trust-saviours-rinchen-wangchuk-tsewang-namgail-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnow%20Leopard%20Conservancy-India%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E%20(SLC-IT)%20%E2%80%94%20and%20his%20successor%20(current%20director%20of%20SLC-IT)%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%2C%20understood%20very%20early%20on%20the%20need%20to%20reconcile%20snow%20leopard%20conservation%20with%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20local%20communities%20who%20lose%20their%20livestock%2C%20particularly%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20to%20these%20elusive%20wild%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20growing%20up%20as%20a%20child%20herder%20in%20the%20picturesque%20Skurbuchan%20village%20in%20Leh%20district%2C%20Dr%20Namgail%20understood%20what%20it%20meant%20for%20local%20communities%20to%20lose%20their%20goats%20and%20sheep%20to%20snow%20leopards.%20This%20is%20something%20even%20the%20late%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%20and%20Jigmet%20Dadul%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20leading%20Snow%20Leopard%20naturalists%20and%20trackers%20%E2%80%94%20also%20understood%20as%20they%20spent%20entire%20winters%20living%20in%20tents%20and%20monitoring%20snow%20leopards%20in%20the%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FRinchen-Wangchuk-500x735.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Late%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FRinchen-Wangchuk-500x735.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FRinchen-Wangchuk-204x300.jpg%20204w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FRinchen-Wangchuk-768x1129.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FRinchen-Wangchuk.jpg%20816w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-246174%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22735%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELate%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20took%20a%20variety%20of%20steps%20to%20address%20the%20needs%20of%20local%20communities%2C%20thus%20addressing%20a%20primary%20source%20of%20snow%20leopard%20deaths%20%E2%80%94%20human-animal%20conflicts.%20These%20steps%20included%20assisting%20local%20farmers%20and%20nomads%20to%20build%20structures%20that%20protect%20their%20livestock%3B%20establishing%20a%20community-controlled%20livestock%20insurance%20programme%3B%20and%20pioneering%20one%20of%20the%20earliest%20models%20of%20eco-tourism%20with%20conservation-linked%20homestays%20located%20in%20critical%20snow%20leopard%20habitats.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConverting%20these%20once-angry%20locals%20into%20active%20conservationists%20is%20no%20mean%20feat.%20Today%2C%20however%2C%20Jigmet%20and%20his%20son%20Nawang%20Gaylston%2C%20run%20a%20wildlife%20expedition%20company%20called%20%E2%80%98The%20Snow%20Leopard%20Quest%E2%80%99%2C%20bringing%20researchers%2C%20conservationists%2C%20and%20tourists%20to%20witness%20this%20majestic%20wild%20cat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKhenrab%20Phuntsog%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F239887%2Fladakh-how-to-track-snow-leopard-rescue-wildlife-guard-khenrab-phuntsog-hemis-national-park-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKhenrab%20Phuntsog%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20an%20award-winning%20snow%20leopard%20conservationist%20with%20over%20two%20decades%20of%20experience%20as%20a%20Wildlife%20Guard%20in%20Hemis%20National%20Park%2C%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%94%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20small%20village%20called%20Chilling.%20He%20was%20barely%2012%20years%20old%20when%20he%20saw%20a%20snow%20leopard%20in%20the%20wild%20barely%20100%20metres%20away%20hunting%20a%20blue%20sheep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FKhenrab-Feature.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Khenrab%20Phuntsog%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FKhenrab-Feature.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FKhenrab-Feature-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FKhenrab-Feature-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FKhenrab-Feature-768x402.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-239904%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKhenrab%20Phuntsog%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20conservationists%20have%20stated%20in%20the%20past%2C%20there%20is%20something%20almost%20mythical%20and%20spiritual%20about%20the%20presence%20of%20snow%20leopards.%20It%E2%80%99s%20something%20Khenrab%20also%20felt%20when%20he%20was%2012%20and%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20this%20vivid%20memory%20he%20had%20of%20a%20snow%20leopard%20would%20inspire%20Khenrab%20to%20dedicate%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life%20to%20protect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20joining%20the%20Wildlife%20Protection%20Department%20in%202000%2C%20he%20has%20rescued%20about%2050%20snow%20leopards%20trapped%20in%20human%20habitations%20and%20released%20them%20back%20into%20the%20wild.%20An%20expert%20in%20installing%20camera%20traps%20and%20tracking%2C%20he%20also%20consults%20private%20operators%20on%20how%20to%20plan%20snow%20leopard%20expeditions%2C%20train%20spotters%20and%20trackers%2C%20and%20leave%20behind%20a%20minimal%20ecological%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKarma%20Sonam%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F264378%2Fkarma-sonam-natwest-group-earth-heroes-award-snow-leopard-himalayan-wolf-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKarma%20Sonam%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20field%20manager%20with%20the%20Nature%20Conservation%20Foundation%20(NCF)%20in%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%94%20has%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20reducing%20human-wildlife%20conflict%20in%2017%20communities%20across%20Eastern%20La