%20like%20snow%20leopards%20and%20wolves%2C%20who%20prey%20on%20their%20livestock.%20Through%20his%20extensive%20grassroots%20efforts%2C%20he%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20to%20repair%20that%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKoustubh%20Sharma%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoustubh%20Sharma%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Conservation%20Science%20Director%20at%20Snow%20Leopard%20Trust%20%E2%80%94%20has%20worked%20in%20some%20of%20the%20remotest%20and%20roughest%20terrains%20in%20the%20world%20to%20better%20understand%20snow%20leopard%20ecology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntroduced%20to%20them%20by%20Dr%20Raghu%20Chundawat%2C%20a%20pioneer%20of%20snow%20leopard%20studies%20in%20India%2C%20Koustubh%20has%20dedicated%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20time%20to%20the%20Global%20Snow%20Leopard%20and%20Ecosystem%20Protection%20Programme.%20The%20programme%2C%20according%20to%20Koustubh%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbrings%20together%20governments%20from%2012%20snow%20leopard%20range%20countries%2C%20policymakers%2C%20institutions%2C%20organisations%20and%20conservationists%20toward%20securing%20the%20future%20of%20snow%20leopards%20and%20their%20mountains%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905-300x238.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905-500x396.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905-768x608.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnow-Leopard-1729605905-150x119.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371719%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20wish%20more%20people%20knew%20about%20conservation%20initiatives%20is%20that%20not%20a%20single%20penny%20of%20the%20money%20meant%20for%20snow%20leopard%20conservation%20goes%20into%20the%20pocket%20of%20the%20snow%20leopards.%20It%20is%20always%20invested%20in%20support%20of%20people%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20the%20local%20or%20indigenous%20communities%20running%20conservation%20programmes%2C%20the%20frontline%20rangers%20patrolling%20and%20monitoring%20wildlife%2C%20or%20the%20conservation%20teams%20working%20under%20expedition%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Koustubh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6our%20initiatives%20are%20about%20much%20more%20than%20just%20protecting%20a%20single%20species.%20We%20work%20closely%20with%20local%20and%20indigenous%20communities%20to%20create%20sustainable%20livelihoods%20that%20benefit%20both%20people%20and%20wildlife.%20When%20we%20invest%20in%20conservation%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20investing%20in%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanctuarynaturefoundation.org%2Farticle%2Fmeet-koustubh-sharma%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESanctuary%20Nature%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsnowleopard.org%2Fmeet-snow-leopard-trusts-new-conservation-science-director-dr-koustubh-sharma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnow%20Leopard%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EShiv%20Kumar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20evening%20in%202019%20when%20Shiv%20Kumar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Deputy%20Range%20Officer%20at%20Lahaul%20forest%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%94%20first%20spotted%20a%20sno