d%20he%20grew%20up%20eating%20in%20Amritsar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20positively%20brimming%20with%20joy%20to%20announce%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebarfis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehad%20the%20desired%20effect%3B%20as%20many%20Indian%20immigrants%20found%20themselves%20transported%20by%20the%20mini%20square-shaped%20time%20capsules%20from%20America%20to%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20festive%20madness%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevered%20on%20the%20culinary%20circuit%2C%20Vikas%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20prowess%20transcends%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20multi-hyphenate%20has%20authored%20over%2037%20books%20%E2%80%94%20with%20his%20most%20recent%20%E2%80%98Imaginary%20Rain%E2%80%99%20(2023)%20being%20turned%20into%20a%20Shabana%20Azmi%20starrer%20%E2%80%94%20has%20directed%20three%20films%20and%20two%20documentaries%3B%20been%20one%20of%20the%20judges%20at%20MasterChef%20India%3B%20and%20helmed%20several%20restaurants%20including%20New%20York%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20%E2%80%98Junoon%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Indian%20restaurants%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357879%2Fmichelin-star-indian-restaurants-avatara-junoon-gaa-veeraswamy-gymkhana-rania-tamarind-semma-benares%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereceive%20the%20coveted%20Michelin%20star%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20this%20compelling%20bio%2C%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20primary%20identifier%20is%20that%20of%20a%20proud%20Indian.%20And%20this%20is%20reflected%20in%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Etadka%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spices%20heated%20in%20hot%20oil)%20that%20makes%20its%20way%20into%20his%20curries%20to%20the%20sparkle%20in%20his%20eyes%20when%20he%20speaks%20about%20life%20back%20in%20his%20beloved%20hometown%2C%20Amritsar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20Vikas%20Khanna%2C%20all%20roads%20lead%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhann