s.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20all%2C%20they%20were%20my%20foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20perfectly%20segues%20his%20next%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20often%20take%20things%20for%20granted%20when%20we%20have%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna%20treasures%20his%20earliest%20memories%20of%20feasting%20on%20the%20food%20prepared%20by%20his%20grandmother%20and%20mother%20%E2%80%94%20experiences%20that%20he%20will%20remember%20forever%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371666%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChef%20Vikas%20Khanna%20treasures%20his%20earliest%20memories%20of%20feasting%20on%20the%20food%20prepared%20by%20his%20grandmother%20and%20mother%20%E2%80%94%20experiences%20that%20he%20will%20remember%20forever%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-8-1729604730.jpg%5C%22