dom%20to%20choose%20what%20you%20want.%20You%20also%20learn%20to%20enjoy%20your%20own%20company%20when%20you%20are%20outdoors%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sangeeth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20happiness%20quotient%20is%20high%20when%20we%20travel%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kavya%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20their%20experiences%20online%20also%20provides%20them%20with%20support.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F306675%2Fanindita-chatterjee-travel-content-creator-new-mom-travelling-with-infant-pregnancy-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuilt%20a%20community%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20supports%20and%20encourages%20us.%20We%20do%20experience%20mental%20breakdowns%20sometimes%3B%20being%20alone%20on%20the%20road%20can%20lead%20to%20self-doubt.%20But%20meeting%20people%20or%20seeing%20positive%20comments%20on%20social%20media%20gives%20us%20the%20boost%20to%20keep%20going.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20dog%20Drogo%20is%20also%20a%20big%20pillar%20of%20support%2C%20providing%20comfort%20and%20alerts%20during%20dangers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20they%20hope%20to%20explore%20more%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20while%20continuing%20their%20mission%20to%20plant%20saplings.%20%E2%80%9CTrue%20happiness%20is%20not%20in%20the%20money%20you%20earn%2C%20but%20in%20the%20experiences%20you%20gather.%20We%20may%20be%20earning%20less%20than%20others%2C%20but%20we%E2%80%99re%20high%20on%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Kavya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20do%20you%20want%20to%20collect%3A%20money%2C%20memories%2C%20or%20both%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Sangeeth%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729588250000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-98-1729585973.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D371590%22%2