le%22%3A%22Legal%20Matters%3A%20An%20Easy-To-Understand%20Summary%20of%20Maternity%20Rights%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImagine%20the%20law%20as%20a%20vast%2C%20intricate%20tapestry%2C%20woven%20with%20threads%20of%20rules%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20statutes.%20Each%20thread%20represents%20a%20different%20aspect%20of%20our%20lives%2C%20from%20the%20contracts%20we%20sign%20to%20the%20rights%20we%20possess.%20Understanding%20this%20complex%20tapestry%20can%20be%20daunting%2C%20but%20it%20is%20essential%20for%20navigating%20the%20challenges%20and%20opportunities%20that%20life%20presents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20series%20aims%20to%20unravel%20the%20legal%20tapestry%2C%20providing%20clear%20and%20concise%20explanations%20of%20various%20laws%20and%20their%20practical%20implications.%20We%20will%20explore%20the%20different%20threads%20that%20make%20up%20this%20intricate%20fabric%2C%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344779%2Fworld-consumers-rights-day-landmark-judgements-consumer-law-in-india-online-orders%2F%5C%22%3Econsumer%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20maternity%20laws%2C%20traffic%20regulations%20to%20employment%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20exploration%20will%20delve%20into%20the%20Maternity%20Benefit%20Act%2C%20a%20crucial%20piece%20of%20legislation%20that%20safeguards%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349558%2Fchennai-sankari-sudhar-job-portal-for-new-mothers-women-with-career-break-overqualified-housewives%2F%5C%22%3Erights%20of%20working%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKey%20provisions%20of%20the%20Maternity%20Benefit%20Act%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaternity%20leave%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMothers%20can%20enjoy%20up%20to%2026%20weeks%20of%20paid%20leave.%20This%20allows%20new%20moms%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20care%20and%20nourishment%20of%20their%20newborns%20without%20compromising%20their%20financial%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBenefits%20for%20commissioning%20mothers%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99re%20a%20commissioning%20mother%2C%20you%20are%20entitled%20to%2012%20weeks%20of%20paid%20leave.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWork-from-home%20option%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENeed%20more%20work%20flexibility%3F%20Under%20the%20Maternity%20Benefits%20Act%2C%20your%20employer%20can%20allow%20you%20to%20work%20from%20home%20for%20a%20period%20of%20time%20after%20you%20have%20availed%20your%20maternity%20leave.%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECr%C3%A8che%20facility%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Companies%20with%2050%20or%20more%20employees%20must%20provide%20cr%C3%A8che%20facilities%20within%20a%20specified%20distance%2C%20helping%20working%20mothers%20balance%20familial%20responsibilities%20while%20staying%20active%20in%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInformation%20about%20benefits%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBefore%20joining%20any%20organisation%2C%20you%20should%20definitely%20inquire%20about%20their%20maternity%20benefits.%20Employers%20are%20required%20to%20inform%20women%20about%20the%20benefits%20available%20under%20the%20Act%20at%20the%20time%20of%20their%20initial%20appointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20does%20this%20law%20apply%20to%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20are%20eligible%20if%20you%20are%20pregnant%20and%20have%20worked%20in%20the%20organised%20sector%20for%20at%20least%2080%20days%20of%20continuous%20service%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20woman%20who%20has%20legally%20adopted%20a%20child%20under%20three%20months%20old.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20woman%20who%20used%20her%20egg%20to%20create%20an%20embryo%20planted%20in%20another%20woman.%20For%20such%20commissioning%20mothers%2C%20the%2012-week%20period%20of%20maternity%20benefit%20is%20calculated%20from%20the%20date%20the%20child%20is%20handed%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%202017%20amendment%2C%20the%20Maternity%20Benefit%20Act%20has%20had%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20working%20women%20in%20India.%20Apart%20from%20bringing%20into%20the%20legal%20framework%20steps%20that%20empower%20women%20to%20continue%20their%20careers%20after%20having%20children%2C%20the%20law%20has%20also%20helped%20improve%20maternal%20and%20child%20health%20outcomes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729523940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D371551%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20series%20aims%20to%20demystify%20complex%20legal%20concepts%20and%20their%20impact%20on%20your%20daily%20life.%20We%20begin%20with%20the%20Maternity%20Benefit%20Act%2C%20a%20crucial%20law%20protecting%20working%20women's%20rights.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Arunava%20Banerjee%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F371551%2Findia-maternity-law-rights-mothers-women-benefits-for-employee-citizens-leave%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IAS%20Sakshi%20Sawhney%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Future%20Tycoons%20Challenge%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20Rural%20%E2%80%98Shark%20Tank%E2%80%99%20for%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Underserved!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmandeep%2C%20holding%20a%20microphone%2C%20stood%20on%20a%20large%20platform%20in%20Punjab.%20Before%20her%2C%20a%20massive%20crowd%2C%20along%20with%20a%20panel%20of%20judges%2C%20MLAs%2C%20and%20government%20officials%2C%20eagerly%20awaited%20her%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20held%20a%20mic%3B%20I%20was%20a%20little%20nervous%20with%20all%20eyes%20on%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amandeep%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20event%20was%20being%20broadcast%20live%20across%20the%20district%20administration%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20platforms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20stepping%20out%20of%20her%20comfort%20